column5: Check your cards 2018 is just about upon us.
GTG , birth  certificate in my wallet says 1950
I need to renew. (2x) 3 year sport and (1x) 3 year small game... Going to be an expensive trip...

2 years ago my loving family bought me a new outdoors card with 1 year fishing for christmas (they didn't realize the problem with this plan).   Id just finished printing out my second 1 year paper license and am thankful that I only have to carry around a beat up, half rotten piece of paper for one more year before I can get a new card & 3 year license.  It sound like the whole licensing system will be changed next year anyway but we'll have to see.
I just went to renew, and I found that I have been expired last year....(oops) and if I order an outdoors card now, it will expire 2020 not 2021. So I will wait for a couple of days.
This got me thinking and checking. But I'm good until this time next year.  Just gotta double check with the rest of my party that will be overnight ice fishing in Feb.
Im good to go as of 10:45 this am.  AND, my spot is ready to fish. Another
